d%20map.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2265b6f07e-2187-4325-8389-bef3f33a2155%5C%22%3EI%20went%20to%20every%20appointment%20with%20the%20fertility%20doctor%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20since%20I've%20always%20been%20a%20problem%20solver%20and%20a%20reverse%20engineer%2C%20I%20thought%2C%20%26quot%3BHow%20can%20we%20approach%20the%20situation%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20had%20no%20luck%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Forthodox-jewish-woman-infertility-iui-pregnancy-secret-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eintrauterine%20insemination%3C%2Fa%3E%20(IUI)%20and%20moved%20on%20to%20IVF.%20The%20process%20was%20pretty%20easy%20from%20a%20male%20perspective%20because%20you%20are%20physically%20removed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20I%20went%20to%20every%20doctor's%20appointment%20to%20listen%20to%20the%20advice.%20It%20was%20hard%20to%20see%20Chloe%20go%20through%20what%20she%20did%2C%20but%20we%20tried%20to%20focus%20on%20the%20end%20result.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20didn't%20share%20our%20journey%20with%20family%20or%20friends%20at%20the%20time.%20It%20was%20to%20protect%20the%20situation%20and%20not%20feel%20like%20we%20were%20letting%20people%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22725%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20family%20of%20four%20on%20a%20dinghy%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6954270f832e0ef1ead6f75d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22544%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMazza%20and%20Melas%20with%20their%20sons.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Brian%20Mazza.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThankfully%2C%20we%20got%20pregnant%20on%20our%20first%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsurance-fertility-ivf-costs-hsa-millennial-couple-infertility-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eround%20of%20IVF%3C%2Fa%3E.%20We%20were%20thrilled%2C%20and%20it%20turned%20into%20elation%20when%20our%20son%2C%20Leo%2C%20was%20born%20in%20July%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20went%20through%20the%20same%20process%2C%20and%20Luke%20arrived%20exactly%20two%20years%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22dcfe75f6-a191-473c-a98a-f397a9fcb056%5C%22%3EI%20advocate%20for%20increased%20awareness%20of%20male%20factor%20infertility%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHolding%20Leo%20and%20Luke%20in%20my%20arms%20was%20every%20dream%20that%20I'd%20ever%20dreamed.%20I'd%20wanted%20to%20become%20a%20father%20so%20much.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20speaking%20up%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhen-facing-infertility-women-are-more-likely-to-blame-themselves-2020-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emale%20factor%20infertility%20%3C%2Fa%3Ebecause%20it's%20a%20topic%20that%20should%20be%20openly%20discussed.%20I%20hope%20that%20I'm%20helping%20to%20remove%20the%20stigma.%20It's%20useful%20when%20someone%20who%20has%20been%20through%20an%20experience%20like%20ours%20can%20share%20their%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20years%20pass%2C%20I%20find%20myself%20gazing%20at%20my%20boys%20%E2%80%94%20now%208%20and%206%20%E2%80%94%20with%20joy%20and%20wonder.%20They're%20bright%2C%20athletic%2C%20and%20kind.%20Chloe%20and%20I%20call%20them%20our%20miracles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fentrepreneur-brian-mazza-low-sperm-count-male-infertility-ivf-2025-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1767127281000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69540e47832e0ef1ead6f478%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fentrepreneur-brian-mazza-low-sperm-count-male-infertility-ivf-2025-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20months%20of%20trying%20for%20a%20baby%2C%20Brian%20Mazza%20learned%20he%20had%20a%20low%20sperm%20count.%20He%20turned%20to%20IVF%20and%20now%20speaks%20openly%20about%20male%20infertility.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Jane%20Ridley)%22%2C%22en