%20aerial%20view%20of%20the%20fold-out%20table%20with%20leaves%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6178216de100ad00181dbbaa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20table%20also%20had%20two%20foldout%20leaves%20for%20more%20counter%20space.%20This%20feature%20came%20in%20handy%20to%20work%20on%20my%20laptop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIn%20some%20roomettes%20%E2%80%94%20mine%20included%20%E2%80%94%20a%20side%20table%20swings%20open%20to%20reveal%20a%20hidden%20toilet.%20Above%20it%2C%20I%20had%20a%20folding%20sink%20and%20mirror.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Side-by-side%20photos%20show%20the%20toilet%20seat%20opened%20and%20closed%20inside%20the%20Amtrak%20roomette.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F616d8c4438c19600183057dc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222249%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20no%20privacy%20curtain%20around%20the%20toilet%2C%20I%20was%20grateful%20to%20be%20a%20solo%20traveler.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EDue%20to%20the%20availability%20when%20I%20booked%20my%20ticket%2C%20I%20had%20to%20switch%20partway%20through%20my%20trip%20to%20another%20roomette%2C%20which%20didn't%20have%20a%20toilet.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Left%3A%20The%20author%20takes%20a%20selfie%20in%20front%20of%20the%20Amtrak%20bathroom%20mirror.%20Right%3A%20The%20author%20brushing%20her%20teeth%20in%20the%20mirror%20of%20her%20roomette%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F616d90d041af0d00193f13e1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222249%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20that%20portion%2C%20