ephen%20Moore%20doesn't%20quite%20agree.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMoore%20served%20as%20one%20of%20Trump's%20chief%20economic%20advisors%20during%20his%20first%20presidency%2C%20working%20with%20the%20administration%20on%20many%20tax%20and%20energy%20policies%2C%20including%20the%20Tax%20Cuts%20and%20Jobs%20Act%20(TCJA)%20of%202017.%20He%20famously%20called%20for%20Trump%20to%20receive%20a%20Nobel%20Peace%20Prize%20in%202018%2C%20citing%2C%20the%20president's%20record%20on%20economic%20policies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20more%20recently%2C%20Moore%20has%20espoused%20a%20different%20perspective.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20recently%20discussed%20his%20take%20on%20Trump's%20economic%20agenda%20for%20both%20the%20past%20and%20coming%20years.%20While%20he%20praised%20the%20president's%20trade%20deals%2C%20he%20noted%20that%20the%20more%20recent%20tariff%20record%20tends%20to%20worry%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20CNBC%20appearance%2C%20Moore%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2Fvideo%2F2025%2F12%2F29%2Fformer-trump-economic-advisor-stephen-moore-on-trump-economy-in-2026.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elaid%20out%3C%2Fa%3E%20how%20he%20feels%20regarding%20the%20past%20year's%20economic%20policies%20and%20their%20impact%2C%20highlighting%20both%20the%20positive%20and%20negative%20impacts%20posed%20by%20Trump's%20trade%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20like%20the%20way%20he's%20been%20able%20to%20negotiate%20better%20deals%20for%20the%20US%2C%26quot%3B%20Moore%20noted%2C%20%26quot%3Bbut%20it%20does%20worry%20me%20with%20tariffs%20because%20tariffs%20do%20have%20a%20negative%20impact%20on%20the%20economy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20acknowledged%20that%20the%20tariffs%20have%20helped%20the%20US%20reach%20trade%20agreements%20with%20nations%20such%20as%20China%20and%20Japan%20but%20noted%20that%20he%20believes%20Trump%20may%20have%20overestimated%20the%20power%20of%20his%20economic%20policies%20when%20he%20promised%20to%20bring%20%2418%20trillion%20into%20th